    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It has been a dependable car, but it is being sold as-is to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 21000.0,
