    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This specimen has been maintained to a rigorous standard, exhibiting consistent mechanical performance and a well-preserved aesthetic. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a refined balance of sophistication and value. Every aspect of this automobile underscores its readiness for immediate service, offering a driving experience that remains both composed and engaging.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
